						<div class="postbody">Just a small progress update. <br /><br />I've added a simple AI! I have not incorporated all the factors that I would like the AI to consider, but I've started on the framework and I think it will do nicely. Turns out that computation time is not really an issue at all. The AI will skip some frames while deciding on the next move, but I think it is hardly noticeable (as some folks had already suggested in an earlier post). It starts to feel slightly more like a game now <img src="./images/smilies/icon_wink.gif" alt=";)" title="Wink" /></div>

